       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. BATCHCT1.
      * CHAIN STEP 1 - SETS THE PENALTY-RUN CONTROL FLAG
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       COPY WSCTLFLG.
       01  WS-CYCLE-DAY              PIC 9(2) VALUE ZERO.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-CYCLE-DAY
           IF WS-CYCLE-DAY = 1
              MOVE 'Y' TO WS-PEN-RUN-FLAG
           END-IF
           DISPLAY 'PENFLAG: ' WS-PEN-RUN-FLAG
           STOP RUN.
